claim.claim-text:
The method of any of the previous claims, wherein generating the alert includes at least one of:
(i) storing the identification of the unauthorized domain and/or a server associated with the unauthorized domain;
(ii) automatically notifying a monitoring system of the identification of the unauthorized domain and/or a server associated with the unauthorized domain;
(iii) notifying the authorized domain of the unauthorized domain; and
(iv) emulating an image request server.
